title: [Post-Black Metal] Inlaid Rust-Machinery In The Dark EP (2007)
description:
Inlaid Rust: Machinery In The Dark [EP-2007] (MP3)
--Black Metal / DOOM / Industrial / Dark Ambient--



Black Metal studio-project from California, USA.
An underground explosion of Avant-Garde sounds
in the vein of Blut Aus Nord, The Axis of
Perdition and the Dark Ambient works of Lustmord.


Track List:
I. Stumble Over Sheeted Dead
II. Steel Screams and Discordance Drone
III. As End-Time As Ash: MMCCX AD (The Inanimate Age)
